      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DIGGER SURE CAN (3) boasts a consistent overall record including seven wins from 20 starts, but missed the frame latest when fourth (25.61) over 450m at this track. Solid record here winning two races. Has the ability and expected to prove tough to beat again. SAMSON'S RIOT (1) turned in a better effort at Grafton last start, finishing third behind Extra Voltage (25.61) in a NG. Chased the leaders and with a clean run can be prominent. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Expected to feature. DESPICABLE MILO (2) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when sixth at this track over 400m behind SIR TICK (22.94) in a Grade 5. Placed at his previous run. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Expected to give a good account. SUNBURNT KEEPER (6) cannot be ruled out.",
